92 /* DesignId : MMWL_DesignId_073 */
93 /* Requirements : AUTORADAR_REQ-768 */
94 rlReturnVal_t rlRfDigMonEnableConfig(rlUInt8_t deviceMap, rlMonDigEnables_t* data)
95 {
96  rlReturnVal_t retVal;
97 
98  /* check if deviceIndex is out of defined value */
99  if ((rlDriverIsDeviceMapValid(deviceMap) != RL_RET_CODE_OK) || (RL_NULL_PTR == data))
100  {
101  /* set return error code */
102  retVal = RL_RET_CODE_INVALID_INPUT;
103  }
104  else
105  {
106  /* Package the command with given data and send it to device */
107  retVal = rlDriverExecuteSetApi(deviceMap, RL_RF_MONITORING_CONF_SET_MSG,
108  RL_RF_DIG_MON_EN_SB, (rlUInt8_t*)data,
109  (rlUInt16_t)sizeof(rlMonDigEnables_t));
110  }
111  return retVal;
112 }

379 /* DesignId : MMWL_DesignId_080 */
380 /* Requirements : AUTORADAR_REQ-861 */
381 rlReturnVal_t rlRfTxPowrMonConfig(rlUInt8_t deviceMap, rlAllTxPowMonConf_t *data)
382 {
383  rlReturnVal_t retVal;
384  /* Initialize Command and Response Sub Blocks */
385  rlDriverMsg_t inMsg;
386  rlDriverMsg_t outMsg = {0};
387  rlUInt16_t numSbc = 0U;
388 
389  /* Initialize Command and Response Sub Blocks */
390  rlPayloadSb_t inPayloadSb[RL_MAX_SB_IN_MSG] = {0};
391 
392  RL_LOGV_ARG0("rlRfTxPowrMonConfig starts...\n");
393 
394  /* Construct command packet */
395  rlDriverConstructInMsg(RL_RF_MONITORING_CONF_SET_MSG, &inMsg, &inPayloadSb[0U]);
396 
397  /* check if deviceIndex is out of defined value */
398  if ((rlDriverIsDeviceMapValid(deviceMap) != RL_RET_CODE_OK) || \
399  (RL_NULL_PTR == data))
400  {
401  retVal = RL_RET_CODE_INVALID_INPUT;
402  RL_LOGE_ARG0("rlRfTxPowrMonConfig, Invalid input \n");
403  }
404  else
405  {
406  /* check for NULL pointer */
407  if ((RL_NULL_PTR != data->tx0PowrMonCfg))
408  {
409  /* Fill in-message Payload */
410  rlDriverFillPayload(RL_RF_MONITORING_CONF_SET_MSG,
411  RL_RF_TX0_POW_MON_CONF_SB,
412  &inPayloadSb[numSbc],
413  (rlUInt8_t* )data->tx0PowrMonCfg,
414  (rlUInt16_t)sizeof(rlTxPowMonConf_t));
415  numSbc++;
416  }
417  /* check for NULL pointer */
418  if ((RL_NULL_PTR != data->tx1PowrMonCfg))
419  {
420  /* Fill in-message Payload */
421  rlDriverFillPayload(RL_RF_MONITORING_CONF_SET_MSG,
422  RL_RF_TX1_POW_MON_CONF_SB,
423  &inPayloadSb[numSbc],
424  (rlUInt8_t* )data->tx1PowrMonCfg,
425  (rlUInt16_t)sizeof(rlTxPowMonConf_t));
426  numSbc++;
427  }
428  /* check for NULL pointer */
429  if ((RL_NULL_PTR != data->tx2PowrMonCfg))
430  {
431  /* Fill in-message Payload */
432  rlDriverFillPayload(RL_RF_MONITORING_CONF_SET_MSG,
433  RL_RF_TX2_POW_MON_CONF_SB,
434  &inPayloadSb[numSbc],
435  (rlUInt8_t* )data->tx2PowrMonCfg,
436  (rlUInt16_t)sizeof(rlTxPowMonConf_t));
437  numSbc++;
438  }
439 
440  if (numSbc > 0U)
441  {
442  /* setting num of sub-block to inMsg */
443  inMsg.opcode.nsbc = numSbc;
444 
445  /* Send Command to mmWave Radar Device */
446  retVal = rlDriverCmdInvoke(deviceMap, inMsg, &outMsg);
447  }
448  else
449  {
450  retVal = RL_RET_CODE_INVALID_INPUT;
451  RL_LOGE_ARG0("sub block is NULL\n");
452  }
453  }
454 
455  return retVal;
456 }

859  rlDriverFillPayload(RL_RF_MONITORING_CONF_SET_MSG,
860  RL_RF_TX2_INT_ANA_SIGNALS_MON_CONF_SB,
861  &inPayloadSb[numSbc],
862  (rlUInt8_t* )data->tx2IntAnaSgnlMonCfg,
863  (rlUInt16_t)sizeof(rlTxIntAnaSignalsMonConf_t));
864  numSbc++;
865  }
866 
867  if (numSbc > 0U)
868  {
869  /* setting num of sub-block to inMsg */
870  inMsg.opcode.nsbc = numSbc;
871 
872  /* Send Command to mmWave Radar Device */
873  retVal = rlDriverCmdInvoke(deviceMap, inMsg, &outMsg);
874  }
875  else
876  {
877  retVal = RL_RET_CODE_INVALID_INPUT;
878  RL_LOGE_ARG0("sub block is NULL\n");
879  }
880  }
881 
882  return retVal;
883 }
